t/uploads/2023/07/barbie-oppenheimer@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/barbie-oppenheimer@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>一部真实的<em>巴本海默</em>电影正在开发中，以利用<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/barbie"><em>芭比</em></a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/oppenheimer"><em>奥本海默</em></a>的双重发行现象。</p><p>这部计划中的喜剧出自 B 片大亨查尔斯·班德之手，他自 20 世纪 70 年代以来一直在制作低成本恐怖喜剧。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/barbie-review-margot-robbie-ryan-gosling-3470019">《芭比娃娃》评论：格蕾塔·葛韦格的成人玩具故事非常有趣</a></strong></li></ul><p>这部电影融合了<em>芭比</em>和<em>奥本海默的</em>故事情节，讲述了科学家娃娃斑比·J·巴本海默博士与男友 Twink Dollman 住在 Dolltopia 的故事。当她冒险进入现实世界并看到娃娃在人类儿童手中受到残酷对待时，巴本海默决定制造一枚巨型核弹来消灭这一切。</p><p>当被问及这是否是无耻的套现时，班德告诉<a href="https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/movies/movie-news/barbenheimer-low-budget-comedy-film-charles-band-1235636257/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《好莱坞报道》</em></a> ：“这是百分百真实的。” “But it&#39;s also an opportunity to have fun with the bizarre coupling of these two movies and the combination of Barbie&#39;s vibe and the darkness of Oppenheimer. You mix that together and you have such an opportunity for dark humour.”</p><p> He added: “It&#39;s so silly. But it seems like every other feature is dark and depressing, and it&#39;s like, God, we need a little humour going into 2024.” </p><figure id="attachment_3473745" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3473745" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3473745" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Barbie_Gosling_Robbie_Dreamhouse.jpg" alt="芭比" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Barbie_Gosling_Robbie_Dreamhouse.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Barbie_Gosling_Robbie_Dreamhouse-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Barbie_Gosling_Robbie_Dreamhouse-800x508.jpg 800w,